464
00:27:52,546 --> 00:27:56,884
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪♪

465
00:28:10,398 --> 00:28:13,734
Did you schedule
a joint session?

466
00:28:14,777 --> 00:28:17,071
[laughs softly]

467
00:28:33,879 --> 00:28:36,005
[Alison sighs]

468
00:28:36,006 --> 00:28:39,134
I feel like there may have been
some changes for you.

469
00:28:39,135 --> 00:28:42,804
Yes, ma'am. You could say that.

470
00:28:42,805 --> 00:28:44,472
So...

471
00:28:44,473 --> 00:28:46,350
where would you like to begin?

